(3966, 237, '_variation_description', '<p>It took CoolTech&trade; weather apparel know-how and lots of wind-resistant fabric to get the Abominable Hoodie just right. It\'s aggressively warm when it needs to be, while maintaining your comfort in milder climes.</p> <p>&bull; Blue heather hoodie.<br />&bull; Relaxed fit. <br />&bull; Moisture-wicking. <br />&bull; Machine wash/dry.</p>'),
