(5541, 333, '_variation_description', '<p>The smooth nylon shell around the Beaumont Summit Kit combats wind, reinforced with a cold-fighting brushed fleece layer. The jacket is reversible, giving you a new look for the return trek. Ample pocket space rounds out this hiker\'s paradise package.</p> <p>&bull; Yellow full zip rain jacket.<br />&bull; Full-zip front. <br />&bull; Stand-up collar. <br />&bull; Elasticized cuffs. <br />&bull; Machine wash/dry.</p>'),
