(332, 1, '2025-09-27 13:18:25', '2025-09-27 13:18:25', '<p>The smooth nylon shell around the Beaumont Summit Kit combats wind, reinforced with a cold-fighting brushed fleece layer. The jacket is reversible, giving you a new look for the return trek. Ample pocket space rounds out this hiker\'s paradise package.</p> <p>&bull; Yellow full zip rain jacket.<br />&bull; Full-zip front. <br />&bull; Stand-up collar. <br />&bull; Elasticized cuffs. <br />&bull; Machine wash/dry.</p>', 'Beaumont Summit Kit', 'This is a variable product called a Beaumont Summit Kit', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'beaumont-summit-kit', '', '', '2025-09-27 13:19:14', '2025-09-27 13:19:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp-ecommerce/?post_type=product&#038;p=332', 0, 'product', '', 0),
